{"tid":343831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友唔想同我搞嘢","createTime":"2017-08-01T19:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:16:36.000Z","uid":26350,"like":6,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e60a25a2914ba39e366ff14bb3cd988c0d70b712","tid":343831,"uid":26350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:25:42.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<br />\n<br />\n我同我男朋友都係18歲<br />\n<br />\n一齊咗一年半<br />\n<br />\n由之前一星期扑2-3次<br />\n<br />\n依加一個月2-3次都唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地係日日都會見面<br />\n<br />\n佢有返pt 我會接佢收工<br />\n<br />\n一得閒就會上去屋企<br />\n<br />\n但呢排佢掂都唔掂下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一掂佢就叫我唔好搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我都係想你掂下我 其實唔一定要搞嘅 <br />\n<br />\n其實打個茄輪都得我都ok架 係街唔會我明 返到屋企kiss下都好難為你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次次有晒feel就話攰 就算搞都好似好唔情願 搞到我迫你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以其實我決定咗算 唔再迫佢 哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢有需要就自然會揾我架啦 係咪？<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係想呻下 希望有人明我haha<br />\n<br />\n利申:藍絲 <br />\n同我好肯定佢一定唔會比<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n仲有唔洗留咩tg 我好愛佢 除咗佢我唔會同第個扑嘢"},{"pid":"feb6dde2868478f7423ad96bf75cedf0ad3ebc2b","tid":343831,"uid":130513,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b9c5a12515acf8c64efd3f5e4cf3beea347de37","tid":343831,"uid":26350,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭雞</blockquote><br />\n你繼續招女扑嘢 冇女你就收聲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be009106348905d31eb814ee7e563c1941202623","tid":343831,"uid":22243,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:34:09.000Z","msg":"扑厭左你就肯定<br />\n另外就要睇下你係咪愈來